---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Start here | ThunderBayAI" description="Start here if you want to understand where AI, CRM, websites, and local SEO fit for your Thunder Bay business.">
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container section-heading">
      <p class="eyebrow">Start here</p>
      <h1>Not sure where to start? Start with the business problem, not the tool.</h1>
      <p class="lead">Most local businesses do not need more AI content. They need clarity on whether their real bottleneck is lead response, follow-up, website conversion, local visibility, or operational drag.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="section" style="padding-top:0;">
    <div class="container grid grid-2">
      <a class="card card-link" href="/ai-opportunity-audit"><h3>Start with the AI Opportunity Audit</h3><p class="muted">Best if you want help identifying where AI or automation could produce the fastest value.</p></a>
      <a class="card card-link" href="/website-audit-thunder-bay"><h3>Start with the Website Audit</h3><p class="muted">Best if you suspect your website, CTA structure, or local SEO foundation is weak.</p></a>
      <a class="card card-link" href="/missed-lead-calculator"><h3>Use the Missed Lead Calculator</h3><p class="muted">Best if you already think slow response and poor follow-up are costing revenue.</p></a>
      <a class="card card-link" href="/services"><h3>Explore service pathways</h3><p class="muted">Best if you already know you want to improve systems, conversion, and local visibility.</p></a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
